{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972590/extras/About.png?t=1734667421\" /><strong>Scolionophobia</strong> is a horror puzzle game where you, a self-proclaimed journalist, are on the hunt for the truth behind the strange disappearances in your town. People have been vanishing without a trace, and whispers point to a sinister connection with the abandoned school. The authorities refuse to investigate the school on the outskirts, dismissing it as mere superstition. So, you decide to take matters into your own hands, only to find yourself trapped within the eerie corridors of that very institution. As you explore the dark and unsettling interiors, you'll soon discover that you're not alone. Do you have the courage to confront your deepest fears and escape this haunted place? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972590/extras/SmartAI.png?t=1734667421\" /><strong>You'll be up against an AI controlled entity that lurks within the school, always watching and waiting. You've stumbled into its territory, and it's hungry for your blood and will stop at nothing to prevent you from escaping.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972590/extras/ThisTHING.png?t=1734667421\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972590/extras/Atmosphere.png?t=1734667421\" /><strong>Throughout every location you explore in Scolionophobia, you will be presented with an eerie and unsettling atmosphere.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/29725